Today - The Smashing Pumpkins
                                        Ok, i looked at the other tab for this song, and i think that it was
a little bit off. This is how i believe the song is really played

intro/theme riff

---11----13----11----15p11------  play this cutesy little riff

------11----11----11-------11---  4x solo, then 8x with band

